---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="BRICS Brokers | Startup-Grade Access to Global & Emerging Markets"
  description="Simple, transparent, and compliant access paths for clients looking beyond traditional boundaries. Market access, execution, and direct support. Registered in the Republic of Kiribati."
  lang="en"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">BRICS Brokers</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">BRICS Brokers – Registered in the Republic of Kiribati</Fragment>

  <section class="bb-hero">
    <div class="bb-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="bb-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="bb-hero-content">
      <h1 class="bb-title">The BRICS Brokers</h1>
      <p class="bb-tagline">Startup-grade access to global and emerging markets.</p>
      <p class="bb-lead">Building simple, transparent, and compliant access paths for clients looking beyond traditional boundaries.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Fast Onboarding</h2>
      <p>Streamlined process designed for speed and clarity. Reach out, identify your needs, complete identity and eligibility checks, and go live with ongoing support.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Global Mindset</h2>
      <p>Focused on emerging and non-traditional markets. FX & macro environments, commodities, equity indices, and digital assets where applicable.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Transparent Structure</h2>
      <p>Clear workflows, no hidden layers. Every step of the process is designed with transparency and compliance at its core.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Human Support</h2>
      <p>Direct contact, real people. Our team provides personalized assistance throughout your journey in global markets.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Market Access & Execution</h2>
      <p>Access to global and emerging markets with reliable execution infrastructure. Client onboarding, reporting, and insights — no financial advice provided.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Compliance First</h2>
      <p>All services are delivered within a compliance-oriented framework, with eligibility checks based on jurisdiction and client profile.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <section class="registration-info">
    <h2>Registration & Legal</h2>
    <p><strong>Registration:</strong> CP-000024</p>
    <p><strong>License:</strong> KBN-90-000002</p>
    <p><strong>Address:</strong> Central Build, Tarawa, Republic of Kiribati</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .bb-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: -40px -20px 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .bb-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/images/bricsbrother.webp');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }
  .bb-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      180deg,
      rgba(0,0,0,.55) 0%,
      rgba(0,0,0,.7) 50%,
      rgba(0,0,0,.85) 100%
    );
  }
  .bb-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    padding: 40px 24px;
  }
  .bb-title {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
    letter-spacing: -.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .bb-tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.95);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
  }
  .bb-lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .bb-title { font-size: 2.4rem; }
    .bb-tagline { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .bb-lead { font-size: 1rem; }
  }
  .registration-info {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .registration-info h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }
  .registration-info p {
    margin: 6px 0;
    color: #555;
  }
</style>
